ntertainment%2F20201027%2FUNMVFGOTFVGVXMCC3AZ2QJ5RNI&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDGaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=d2e454d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201027%2FUNMVFGOTFVGVXMCC3AZ2QJ5RNI&h=5e0b803a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201027/UNMVFGOTFVGVXMCC3AZ2QJ5RNI</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T00:59:10.000Z","msg":"Sir，你點知的"},{"pid":"d03462a450a554410ac3b6e16b6246ec5620dbe2","tid":2260794,"uid":54975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:00:03.000Z","msg":"告得入/重嘅話大波華就介入撤控啦，需家擺明小事咪做下戲扮有法治囉。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6786d3e8770f6d049f2cc0a5e3f09a0cf3994d","tid":2260794,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:01:49.000Z","msg":"W"},{"pid":"f9537882c1d3e5575375fff563e546fdcee98d21","tid":2260794,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a068f1c10a124df004ca8ff6bf9f4c84695b320d","tid":2260794,"uid":107681,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T00:57:21.000Z","msg":"鳩蛇不如係狗屋私了佢，我地咩都睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:01:50.000Z","msg":"我都唔係警察，唔係狗，黑白警都唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055ab82b3446bd75ef4c7ac7866c575ca8cd0477","tid":2260794,"uid":91604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1284c20cce77ccdeca5254998b859657afdcefd1","tid":2260794,"uid":43785,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff0edbf451e90f29a0d4510a3371d07ce7edf2f2","tid":2260794,"uid":25973,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T00:39:20.000Z","msg":"其實佢咁樣繼續無後果 一定會繼續醉駕 有朝一日分分鐘撞死人架wor 到陣時 其實呢班控方全部都有份殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T00:41:43.000Z","msg":"應該唔會啦，可以利用嘅都利用曬。<br />\n下次斷正真係要坐監了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:02:18.000Z","msg":"下次唔斷正咪得囉"},{"pid":"e7fef826b48bb749241f7bd2267875c2e3fe35fb","tid":2260794,"uid":64576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:02:59.000Z","msg":"醉駕?"},{"pid":"d06612a30604a5271864064c82a78edf7dd864f5","tid":2260794,"uid":113494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:03:34.000Z","msg":"原來醉駕只要唔做呼氣測試就可以告條輕罪<br />\n學到野了"},{"pid":"58730597b41e369916fee0c3c72dbd6163e7f10a","tid":2260794,"uid":132698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"764595d3a32c49449ede857d894fc93e3fe76ec6","tid":2260794,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T00:29:39.000Z","msg":"楊明俾人告三單野分別係「門窗玻璃透光度不足」、「拒絕提供血液樣本以作化驗」及「不小心駕駛」<br />\n<br />\n「門窗玻璃透光度不足」，不值一提。<br />\n<br />\n因為佢冇做酒精呼氣測試，所以唔可以再告多佢一次重犯醉駕，只能改告拒絕提供血液樣本以作化驗。<br />\n由於「拒絕提供血液樣本以作化驗」係初犯，所以係庭上只要認罪，有悔意，有人求情，基本上停2-3年牌，罰少少錢了事，唔使坐監。<br />\n<br />\n「不小心駕駛」情況同上，楊明摧毀咗古蹟我唔明點解唔撚告「危險駕駛」。<br />\n<br />\n仲有佢摧毀咗古蹟，點解唔撚告「刑毀」，我發現檢控提告嗰邊其實好撚有問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n---------------------<br />\n<br />\n所以份劇本就係，<br />\n楊明係初犯，在庭上認罪，向大家表示有悔意，大量求情信，最後罰錢加停牌，唔使坐監。<br />\n<br />\n我話你知，只要有背景，識玩程序，你醉駕都可以唔洗坐監。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家可以google搜尋公益金董事，蔡寶健<br />\n<br />\n早幾年蘋果拍曬片，擺明醉駕，只要唔吹波，都唔使坐監，有曬案例。<br />\n估計楊明同佢都係一樣結果。<br />\n<br />\n當然啦，我希望有例外，就係楊明要入去坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過可能性相當低。<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:05:07.000Z","msg":"只要認定係「意外」<br />\n就唔會有刑毀既可疑性<br />\n就算你撞爛乜都好話知你世界級古物"},{"pid":"ea654148fa9ce229b12733ed4d93ccd17b6c3737","tid":2260794,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:05:28.000Z","msg":"東區庭實搵鄭紀航審<img src=